{"tid":1561450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我希望大家重新諗下和理非 係邊種和","createTime":"2019-09-11T15:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T07:14:28.000Z","uid":81909,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"85d75250276af55e1e51fcaca9840cda11d733c0","tid":1561450,"uid":81909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:09:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">雖然話和勇不分 <br />\n<br />\n但一直以嚟和理非嘅和 都係講緊打文宣戰 眾籌登報 經濟制裁 用twitter reddit 將件事推上國際層面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連儂牆係好靚 好感動 但我地目的係咩？打氣？文宣？我地嘅對象又係邊個？ 老實講有時見到一堆海報只係花多眼亂 路人亦都唔會有心機慢慢睇 大字報或者係重覆嘅活動文宣會更有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唱國歌同10點鳩叫為團結民眾同打氣絕對冇問題 但唔可以係主線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢排啲主要活動post都沉得好快 唔排除有人帶風向 連毛EE post 都推唔到上去 <br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可重新諗下 究竟我地係想得到咩 <br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">共產黨係比惡魔更惡魔 絕對唔可以鬆懈<br />\n</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n祝大家武運昌盛<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"6b5e76d45b9f05913e900e129922718c90eb1897","tid":1561450,"uid":81909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3e2673108cfde7c75fbe4878e0edddc2b0e11133","tid":1561450,"uid":5682,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:09:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 遮打見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig